        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7607",
        "content": "Chap. twenty one.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7607_89899_000000_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7607/89899/7607_89899_000000_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7607",
        "content": "How the Abbot Ceolfrid sent master builders to the King of the Picts to build a church, and with them an epistle concerning the Catholic Easter and the Tonsure.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7607_89899_000000_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7607/89899/7607_89899_000000_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7607",
        "content": "[seven ten a d]",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7607_89899_000001_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7607/89899/7607_89899_000001_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7607",
        "content": "To the end that he might bring this to pass with the more ease and greater authority, he sought aid from the English, whom he knew to have long since framed their religion after the example of the holy Roman Apostolic Church.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7607_89899_000002_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7607/89899/7607_89899_000002_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7607",
        "content": "For we know, that whensoever the lords of this world labour to learn, and to teach and to guard the truth, it is a gift of God to his Holy Church.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7607_89899_000003_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7607/89899/7607_89899_000003_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7607",
        "content": "\"There are then three rules given in the Sacred Writings, whereby the time of keeping Easter has been appointed for us and may in no wise be changed by any authority of man; two whereof are divinely established in the law of Moses; the third is added in the Gospel by reason of the Passion and Resurrection of our Lord.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7607_89899_000003_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7607/89899/7607_89899_000003_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7607",
        "content": "For the law enjoined, that the Passover should be kept in the first month of the year, and the third week of that month, that is, from the fifteenth day to the one and twentieth.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7607_89899_000003_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7607/89899/7607_89899_000003_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7607",
        "content": "It is added, by Apostolic institution, from the Gospel, that we are to wait for the Lord's day in that third week, and to keep the beginning of the Paschal season on the same.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7607_89899_000003_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7607/89899/7607_89899_000003_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7607",
        "content": "Which threefold rule whosoever shall rightly observe, will never err in fixing the Paschal feast.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7607_89899_000004_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7607/89899/7607_89899_000004_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7607",
        "content": "In the first month, on the fourteenth day of the month, ye shall eat unleavened bread, until the one and twentieth day of the month at even.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7607_89899_000004_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7607/89899/7607_89899_000004_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7607",
        "content": "Seven days shall there be no leaven found in your houses.' Now, who is there that does not perceive, that there are not only seven days, but rather eight, from the fourteenth to the one and twentieth, if the fourteenth be also reckoned in the number?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7607_89899_000004_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7607/89899/7607_89899_000004_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7607",
        "content": "For it is in truth the third week, because it begins on the evening of the fourteenth day, and ends on the evening of the one and twentieth.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7607_89899_000005_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7607/89899/7607_89899_000005_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7607",
        "content": "In the first day ye shall have an holy convocation.'",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7607_89899_000006_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7607/89899/7607_89899_000006_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7607",
        "content": "For on whichever of those days it shall fall, Easter will be rightly kept on the same; seeing that it is one of those seven days on which the feast of unleavened bread is commanded to be kept.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7607_89899_000006_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7607/89899/7607_89899_000006_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7607",
        "content": "Thus it comes to pass that our Easter never falls either before or after the third week of the first month, but has for its observance either the whole of it, to wit, the seven days of unleavened bread appointed by the law, or at least some of them.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7607_89899_000007_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7607/89899/7607_89899_000007_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7607",
        "content": "\"The catholic reason of this observance being thus explained, the unreasonable error, on the other hand, of those who, without any necessity, presume either to anticipate, or to go beyond the term appointed in the Law, is manifest.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7607_89899_000008_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7607/89899/7607_89899_000008_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7607",
        "content": "And both sorts are mistaken, not only in fixing and computing the moon's age, but also sometimes in finding the first month; but this controversy is longer than can be or ought to be contained in this letter.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7607_89899_000008_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7607/89899/7607_89899_000008_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7607",
        "content": "I will only say thus much, that by the vernal equinox, it may always be found, without the chance of an error, which must be the first month of the year, according to the lunar computation, and which the last.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7607_89899_000008_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7607/89899/7607_89899_000008_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7607",
        "content": "And that this must be so, there is this cogent reason.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7607_89899_000008_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7607/89899/7607_89899_000008_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7607",
        "content": "But if the full moon shall happen to be but one day before the time of the equinox, the aforesaid reason proves that such moon is not to be assigned to the first month of the new year, but rather to the last of the preceding, and that it is therefore not meet for the celebration of the Paschal festival.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7607_89899_000011_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7607/89899/7607_89899_000011_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7607",
        "content": "We therefore forbear to send you these same cycles of the times to come, because, desiring only to be instructed respecting the reason for the Paschal time, you show that you have enough of those catholic cycles concerning Easter.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7607_89899_000012_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7607/89899/7607_89899_000012_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7607",
        "content": "\"But having said thus much briefly and succinctly, as you required, concerning Easter, I also exhort you to take heed that the tonsure, concerning which likewise you desired me to write to you, be in accordance with the use of the Church and the Christian Faith.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7607_89899_000012_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7607/89899/7607_89899_000012_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7607",
        "content": "Behold then how each of these men of God differed in the manner of their appearance abroad, though their inward consciences agreed in a like grace of virtue.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7607_89899_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7607/89899/7607_89899_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7607",
        "content": "\"But do not think that I have said thus much, as though I judged them worthy to be condemned who use this tonsure, if they uphold the catholic unity by their faith and works; nay, I confidently declare, that many of them have been holy men and worthy servants of God.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7607_89899_000014_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7607/89899/7607_89899_000014_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7607",
        "content": "He would also have been mindful to amend the tonsure, if his influence had availed so far.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7607_89899_000015_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7607/89899/7607_89899_000015_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7607",
        "content": "The grace of the eternal King preserve you in safety, long reigning for the peace of us all, my dearly beloved son in Christ.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    }
]